    "en": {
      "title": "4 more Covid deaths",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Director General of Health Services confirmed this afternoon (26) that four more people infected with 'Covid' have died yesterday (25).",
        "The Director General of Health Services states that three of the four dead people are over 60 years of age and a woman between the ages of 30 and 59 is among them.",
        "The director general of health services further mentioned that there are three men and a woman among the four dead people."
      ],
